{"tid":1106455,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"曾美慧孜《三夫》奪最佳女主角 哽咽感謝張國榮","createTime":"2019-04-14T14:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T05:29:31.000Z","uid":82917,"like":185,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"1e36fd5961f7d9d53cc474f01a7f2fcd1b8bf7e0","tid":1106455,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T14:51:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">大家都好掛住你呀哥哥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/14/224936_eda1a470cc2cf82f4e31f9e49e2209b7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F14%2F224936_eda1a470cc2cf82f4e31f9e49e2209b7.png&h=390bf8f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今屆金像獎提名最佳女主角有曾美慧孜《三夫》、蔡卓妍《非分熟女》、余香凝《非同凡響》、Crisel Consunji《淪落人》及張靜初《無雙》。由三位影后惠英紅、鮑起靜及毛舜筠頒發「最佳女主角」，最後由曾美慧孜奪得影后！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5c6bAEW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5c6bAEW.png&h=fd5d4c9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在宣布得獎時，得知自己得獎的曾美慧孜心情激動，在台上哽咽說出感謝辭。她先用廣東話感謝導演陳果和一眾幕後工作人員，然後感激來到現場的母親一直對自己的堅持，並表示要感謝已故巨星張國榮。小美透露《三夫》在去年4月1日開機，而從來未來過香港的她就從九龍坐的士去港島文華酒店，但因為身上只得500元港幣，不夠錢來回九龍及港島而被該的士司機拒載，不過最後都到達了文華酒店現場悼念哥哥：「我要感謝張國榮，他給了我很大的鼓勵，從他身上我學會了戲比天大。」即使遇到困難，還要繼續堅持。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u0jc4xE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu0jc4xE.png&h=01db7797&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/14/224906_0ea755ae08527526773c97d8db32e975.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F14%2F224906_0ea755ae08527526773c97d8db32e975.png&h=cfba15ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />恭喜小美 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n多謝你用廣東話致詞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCredits: HK01"},{"pid":"5e762ab21de4b128143f2797179a667e3c249c6f","tid":1106455,"uid":110018,"like":31,"dislike":3,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T14:51:40.000Z","msg":"實至名歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52bda099b984674025217cddc14beb01941f625b","tid":1106455,"uid":219194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T14:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b867ea3cf06a0a69ce5bfcd4baa74a71741ee3","tid":1106455,"uid":183383,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T14:52:35.000Z","msg":"有張國榮=有小美(樓主)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df26da15326afe18051ef00d1c047dc16e2f8503","tid":1106455,"uid":82917,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11b867ea3cf06a0a69ce5bfcd4baa74a71741ee3","tid":1106455,"uid":183383,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T14:52:35.000Z","msg":"有張國榮=有小美(樓主)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T14:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\